In a certain code language, ‘lit pae hon’ means ‘mango is red’, ‘pae to nap’ means ‘red and blue’ and ‘to hon da’ means ‘frock is blue’. Which of the following represents ‘mango’ in that language? </br> एक निच्शित कूटभाषा में, ‘lit pae hon’ अर्थात ‘mango is red’, ‘pae to nap’  अर्थात red and blue और ‘to hon da’ अर्थात ‘frock is blue’ निम्न में से कौन सा उस कूटभाषा में को दर्शाता है@lit@to@nap@pae@1@